Uses of Package
com.example.rubank

  • Classes in com.example.rubank used by com.example.rubank
    Class
    Description
    Account
    Account class represents an account as an object with a profile and balance, and is the general type of the other account types.
    AccountDatabase
    AccountDatabase class stores Account objects in an array, and provides methods to open, close, withdraw/deposit from/to an account, and sort then print accounts.
    Campus
    Campus enum class represents a campus as a campus code (0, 1, or 2).
    Checking
    Checking class inherits from Account class and represents a checking account with a profile and balance.
    Date
    Date class represents a calendar date as an object with a year, month, and day.
    Profile
    Profile class represents a holder's profile as an object with a first name, last name, and date of birth.
    Savings
    Savings class inherits from Account class and represents a saving account with a profile, balance, and loyalty status.
